1:02:51.435 --> 1:02:53.767
For helping
getting him settled back here.

1:02:56.106 --> 1:02:57.266
I don't mind.

1:02:58.817 --> 1:02:59.852
[WENDY SIGHS]

1:03:02.362 --> 1:03:04.603
