1:03:04.781 --> 1:03:06.897
Sounds nice.

1:03:13.206 --> 1:03:15.367
Jesus.

1:03:17.544 --> 1:03:19.751
Hey, buddy.

1:03:20.213 --> 1:03:21.419
What are you doing up?

1:03:21.590 --> 1:03:24.002
