1:03:29.681 --> 1:03:30.716
Come here.

1:03:39.316 --> 1:03:41.181
Here you go, buddy.

1:03:43.737 --> 1:03:47.730
Thank you.
You're welcome.

1:03:56.791 --> 1:03:58.531
Why don't you sit down for a minute?

1:04:09.221 --> 1:04:12.213
I wanna tell you something, Abel.

1:04:12.641 --> 1:04:16.179
And I want you to try
to really understand, okay?

1:04:16.353 --> 1:04:18.514
Okay.

1:04:20.023 --> 1:04:22.730
