1:04:48.969 --> 1:04:52.336
Do you know whose tummy
that was?

1:04:53.932 --> 1:04:56.298
It was Wendy's.

1:04:57.811 --> 1:05:00.473
Wendy was your first mommy.

1:05:01.856 --> 1:05:04.472
You came out of her tummy.

1:05:13.577 --> 1:05:16.364
That's kind of crazy, right?

1:05:16.580 --> 1:05:21.165
You see, Daddy and Wendy,
we used to be married.

1:05:21.668 --> 1:05:24.250
But we realized that...

1:05:24.421 --> 1:05:26.707
...we were better offjust being friends.

1:05:29.301 --> 1:05:32.384
But that's why she's here now.

1:05:33.138 --> 1:05:37.097
To help take care of you
now that you need a mommy.

1:05:38.602 --> 1:05:39.682
Okay?

1:05:43.231 --> 1:05:47.975
I just want you to know there are
so many people that love you, Abel.

1:05:48.278 --> 1:05:50.519
No matter what happens...

1:05:50.697 --> 1:05:54.906
...you're always gonna have
a daddy and a mommy...

1:05:55.577 --> 1:05:58.364
...that are gonna do their best for you.

1:06:03.668 --> 1:06:05.374
Hey.

1:06:05.920 --> 1:06:08.753
You wanna ask me anything, baby?

1:06:09.633 --> 1:06:11.589
No.

1:06:13.928 --> 1:06:16.510
Well, we can talk about it
whenever you want.

1:06:17.515 --> 1:06:18.971
Or not.

1:06:19.142 --> 1:06:21.178
Okay? It's up to you.

1:06:24.564 --> 1:06:26.304
All right.

1:06:27.317 --> 1:06:29.308
Why don't you go get back into bed?

1:06:29.486 --> 1:06:31.727
I'll come in in a minute
and tuck you in.

1:06:45.377 --> 1:06:47.368
Oh, buddy.

1:06:48.838 --> 1:06:50.624
Good night.

1:06:56.137 --> 1:06:57.388
[WENDY SIGHS]

