1:08:45.622 --> 1:08:49.035
Good night. Get some sleep.

1:08:49.709 --> 1:08:51.040
Daddy.

1:08:52.587 --> 1:08:54.123
Yeah?

1:08:54.297 --> 1:08:57.960
ls Wendy my first mommy...

1:08:58.134 --> 1:09:02.798
